# ==============================================================================
# backup_validation.conf — list of VMs to validate (full cycle mode)
#
# Install as: /root/backup_validation.conf
#
# One VM per line. Three fields, separated by semicolons:
#   vmid : mode : overrides   (shown here with : to avoid the real separator)
#
#   vmid       Original VMID of the VM whose latest PBS backup will be restored
#   mode       auto | hybrid | manual   (default auto if omitted)
#                - auto    only auto-discovered services are validated
#                - hybrid  auto-discovered services plus overrides
#                - manual  only the services listed in overrides
#   overrides  service:port,service:port   (used in hybrid/manual)
#                port 0 = skip the port/HTTP check (systemd check only)
#
# Lines starting with a hash and blank lines are ignored.
# Save with LF (Unix) line endings.
# ==============================================================================

# vmid ; mode   ; overrides
105    ; auto   ;
110    ; hybrid ; cloudflared:0
210    ; manual ; myapp:8080
